node.text: The highly-anticipated album is now set to release on August 15. The date was confirmed by an iTunes album preview page. node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: @baitme and @adidas Consortium have reunited for a collaborative 'Cowboy Bebop' Matchplay. The tribute sneakers feature black smooth leather uppers with mismatched neon green and yellow branding as well as mismatched heel tabs. Other details include 'Cowboy Bebop' branding on the heel counter in Japanese and English paired with a trio of lace options, black, neon green, and yellow. The collection also consists of apparel ranging from tees to hoodies. The raffle is open now until September 18.⁠⁠
Photo: BAIT

node.text:
@hypebeastwatches: @jacobandco has released its first trio of minute repeaters in a sapphire crystal case as part of the company’s Twin Turbo Furious collection. Each timepiece not only features a fully transparent sapphire crystal case but a decimal minute repeater, a first in the world of luxury watches. Each hypercar-inspired colorway is limited to six pieces. Hit the link in bio to learn more.⁠⁠
Photo: Jacob & Co.

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: New images of the upcoming @supremenewyork x @nikesb Dunk High has surfaced. Dubbed the "By Any Means" the first of the duo of high-top features a "Black/White" leather base that's accented by a number of New York City-themed embellishments. Additionally, “Supreme Team” is subtly embroidered in white behind the heel tab, while red insoles add a cut-off “Sup” graphic for a final dash of branded flair. Hit the link in bio for details.⁠⁠
Photo: Nike

@hypebeaststyle: @nonnative has tapped @gramicci for a trio of GORE-TEX INFINIUM infused climber easy pants, a first for the silhouette. Alongside the collaborative pants, nonnative has also dressed a lightweight Stroller Pullover and a pocket-heavy Trooper Jacket in the higly-functional technology. @hypebeastmusic: Start your week with HYPEBEAST Sounds, our ongoing playlist that rotates through 50 of our editors’ current favorite tracks. Swipe to check out some of this week’s highlights and hit the link in bio for the rest. What are you listening to?⁠⁠
Video: Isabella Chon/HYPEBEAST

node.text:
@hypefoods: Nissin is continuing to celebrate its 50th anniversary, this time with its new Cup Noodle Sodas. Featured in the release are the Cup Noodle Soda, Seafood Soda, Curry Soda and Chili Tomato Soda. Pre-order a set from September 13 to 17 on Nissin's official website. Would you try this?⁠
Photo: Nissin

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: Here's a first look at @patta_nl's upcoming @nike Air Max 1 "Monarch." The sneaker comes in pops of autumnal tones and houses a reworked mudguard which boasts an embroidered Swoosh towards the front. Keep an eye out for official release details.⁠
Photo: @der_alex_07

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 14, 2021. May be an anime-style image.

node.text:
#hypeAF: A 1/7-scale version of the life-size Satoru Gojo statue that was on display at the “Anime Jujutsu Kaisen Exhibition” in Japan has been made. The toy features Satoru Gojo posed on his domain chair where the height of his seated position also matches up with things like paper cups and cup noodles, allowing one to pose the figure on a number of everyday household items. Head over to F: NEX to reserve one now.⁠⁠
Photo: MAPPA

@hypebeastkicks: The Air Jordan 1 High OG “Patent Bred” will be arriving with special packaging according to new imagery. As part of @jumpman23’s upcoming Holiday 2021 Retro collection, the two-tone patent leather shoe comes with a matching retro “Nike” Jordan Brand box that has a glossy finish and a metallic red Jumpman hangtag. Look for it to drop on December 30 for $170 USD.⁠⁠

node.text:
#HBFits: Fashion's biggest night, the #MetGala, returns after a one year hiatus with the theme "In America", in reference to the forthcoming "In America: A Lexicon of Fashion" exhibit at the @metmuseum. @blonded stole the show with a lime green robot baby as his partner, @lilnasx opted for a buffed up C-3PO look, while @asaprocky and @badgalriri got cozy with a puffy ensemble. Swipe for some of our favourite looks. ⁠⁠
Photos: Mike Coppola/Arturo Holmes/Dimitrios Kambouris/Kevin Mazur/Theo Wargo/Getty Images
